An '''airsmith''' is an airflow [[technician]] who engineers, designs, builds, and repairs high pressure [[air pump]]s and [[compressors]] for practical use.
Equipment used or dealt with can include: *[[SCBA]] (self contained breathing apparatus) *Pneumatic [[jackhammer]]s *High pressure tanks.
An air conditioning & heating technician would be an example of an airsmith.
